                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Inquiet, prêt à se troubler,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ce martyr murmure : Il me semble",
