                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "A présent, son pauvre cœur tremble.\nInquiet, prêt à se troubler,\nCe martyr murmure : Il me semble\nQue je voudrais bien m'en aller."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mais Scribe, qu'un laurier décore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Apparaît dans les airs flottants",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et dit à Landrol : Reste encore.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Landrol répond : Combien de temps ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais Scribe, qu'un laurier décore,\nApparaît dans les airs flottants\nEt dit à Landrol : Reste encore.\nLandrol répond : Combien de temps ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Mais, blêmi par de tristes rages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Scribe prend un air solennel.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et l'on voit passer des orages",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sur le front de ce colonel.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, blêmi par de tristes rages,\nScribe prend un air solennel.\nEt l'on voit passer des orages\nSur le front de ce colonel."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Des Cunégondes et des Thècles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Passent, mystérieux témoins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Dans ses yeux clairs. — Trois mille siècles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Dit-il. Ou quatre. Plus ou moins.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Des Cunégondes et des Thècles\nPassent, mystérieux témoins,\nDans ses yeux clairs. — Trois mille siècles,\nDit-il. Ou quatre. Plus ou moins."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Landrol dit : Mais quoi ! la vallée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Frissonnante de Josaphat",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Délivrera mon âme ailée.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Mais feu Scribe lui répond : Fat !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Landrol dit : Mais quoi ! la vallée\nFrissonnante de Josaphat\nDélivrera mon âme ailée.\nMais feu Scribe lui répond : Fat !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Quand on résiste, je m'obstine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
